  "subject": "Simplify maven version numbering",
  "commit_message": "Simplify maven version numbering\n\nInstead of hard-coding version number of artifacts in pom files, use\nthe maven property , which can then be passed as a command\nline argument from Jenkins jobs. In this way, we do not need to remember\nto roll snapshot versions in each pom.xml after a repo is released.\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3563\nSigned-off-by: Dan Timoney <dtimoney@att.com>\nChange-Id: Ia91da0b4403d1b07eb87c555824a8231aed6f6c5\n",
